item.title: Trans Resources
item.description: General Resources These resources cover a lot of ground. They don’t focus on one thing, or they deal with more general concerns. LGBT Near Me This site helps you locate Trans and other Queer resources in your area. That’s Gender Dysphoria FYI This resource is aimed at questioning trans folks. Does a good job providing an inside look at the trans experience. Transfem Science Provides good summaries of the scientific literature concerning MTF transitions.
